{
  "stem": "3631.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But that was really the only thing that they did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the other thing was that we had a lot of assemblies, and during Hitler time, of course, a lot of German songs, the German national anthem, and the and the other Hitler songs were being played.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I didn't like this too much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And where-- whenever you had to greet, you had to raise your arm.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so I played the kettle-- kettle drums in the school orchestra, and I had a good excuse not to have to stand up and raise my arm, sing with them.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I just did my kettle-drums.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were very few students.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In high-- during my whole high school times, there was only about maybe two Jewish students in a class.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [LAUGHS] I couldn't really answer that question.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew what-- we read the papers, of course, and we started hearing about the restrictions, about the things that started going on.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I want to tell you, in the high school, there was a-- we were not allowed, as Jews, to go in the public swimming pool, even though this was built by a Jewish philanthropist in the city.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were excluded from-- from certain outings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Every year, they had a-- an annual like a-- like a little Olympic Games between all the-- between all the high schools.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Each schools marched in the stadium, and it was a contest in the different subjects of-- of sports, different types of sports, and they marched around with our school colors.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were excluded to participate or even to watch.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as 12, 13 year olds, something, that's something that hurt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was a-- I loved to ride the bicycle.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did a lot of bicycle riding.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
